com.wordnik.swagger.annotations

Annotation Type Api


  • @Target(value=TYPE)
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface Api
    describes a top-level api. Classes with @Api annotations will be included in the Resource Listing: https://github.com/wordnik/swagger-core/wiki/Resource-Listing for details
